        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Steam-powered torpedo boat developed in the early 20th century, and used in the First World War, a development of the torpedo boat destroyer, and distinct from the motor torpedo boat of WWII.</skos:scopeNote>
        <dcterms:publisher rdf:resource="http://www.historicengland.org.uk"/>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:narrower>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A small warship built to operate close to the shore or in river estuaries. Used for shore bombardment and patrol duties.</skos:scopeNote>
